### 5. 🟢 Memory Leaks: Stream cleanup — mostly handled

**File:** [useStreamClient.js](file:///c:/Users/asmit/Desktop/SEM%206%20Project/talent-IQ/frontend/src/hooks/useStreamClient.js#L67-L79)

**Current status:** The cleanup IIFE properly calls `videoCall.leave()`, `chatClientInstance.disconnectUser()`, and [disconnectStreamClient()](file:///c:/Users/asmit/Desktop/SEM%206%20Project/talent-IQ/frontend/src/lib/stream.js#27-37). This is **adequate** for normal usage.

**Minor concern:** The IIFE async cleanup isn't awaited by React, so if the user navigates away very fast, the promises may not finish. This is a known React limitation and is acceptable — the Stream SDK handles this gracefully.

**No code change needed** — just noted for awareness.

